title: Detectives appeal for witnesses following Magherafelt fire (PSNI - Police Service of Northern Ireland)
text: ( Source : PSNI - Police Service of Northern Ireland ) 11 Oct 2015 Detectives are investigating a suspicious fire at a quarry in Magherafelt . The blaze inside a building at Hogg's Quarry on Tobermore Road was reported to police at about 9.45pm
